    "The entire workflow of proposed multimodal ML algorithms is depicted in Figure 1 which includes following steps: a.",
    "Data collection and preparation: the dataset primarily comprises images, encompassing both real-time images captured with mobile cameras and JPEG files obtained online.",
    "These images undergo preprocessing to a format suitable for subsequent analysis. b.",
    "Choice of deep learning (DL) models: this step involves selecting the appropriate DL models for training.",
    "In the current work, the visual geometry group-16 (VGG-16), a CNN-based model, is employed for image processing, while LSTM and Transformer-based models handle textual data processing."
